snippet.title: Best VGM 2170 - Zelda : Link's Awakening - First Time on Koholint (Sword Search)
snippet.description:

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

Gameboy

First Time on Koholint (Sword Search)
Yuichi Ozaki, Kazumi Totaka, Minako Hamano & Kazue Ishikawa
